	"description": "A step by step approach towards visualizing financial datasets\nIt is a challenge to communicate data and display these visualizations on\nmultiple devices and platforms.\n\n&gt; “Data is just like crude. It’s valuable, but if unrefined it cannot really be\nused.” - Michael Palmer\n[https://ana.blogs.com/maestros/2006/11/data_is_the_new.html]\nD3 (Data-Driven Documents) solves this age-old dilemma. It provides developers\nand analysts the ability to build customized visualizations for the Web with\ncomplete",
